songs.title: Shakal pe mat ja
songs.lyrics:
Ho assi fateechar bhukhe nange saatho taan mangde hi changge
Free fund vich pai gaye pange tuhi bach lai har har gange
Bhukhe nange..
Assi fateechar bhukhe nange saatho taan mangde hi changge
Free fund vich pai gaye pange tuhi bach lai har har gange
Meri shakal pe mat ja pandu, main kya hoon tujhe bata doon
Bholi bali surat par shakal pe mat ja
Meri shakal pe mat ja pandu, main kya hoon tujhe bata doon
Bholi bali surat par shakal pe mat ja
Gasmandus.. oh zandu

Aapa taan badey nikamme, vele paye rehnde lamme
Saanu taan samajh nai aundi, aapa kis kamm lai jamme
Assi fateechar bhukhe nange saatho taan mangde hi changge
Free fund vich pai gaye pange tuhi bach lai har har gange
Meri shakal pe mat ja pandu, main kya hoon tujhe bata doon
Bholi bali surat par shakal pe mat ja
Meri shakal pe mat ja pandu, main kya hoon tujhe bata doon
Bholi bali surat par shakal pe mat ja

Let me tell you the story
Chaar yaar chhichhore
Nikle tigdam ladane bina baat ke lag gaye laude
Tune abhi dekha nahin, dekha hai toh jaana nahin
Jaana hai toh maana nahin, hume pehchaana nahin
.. rakh dunga lekin meri warning hai yeh koi gaana nahin
Shakal pe mat ja, akal se darr
Itna na kar tu agar magar
Mummy kasam teri ek karke rakh dunga sister-mother
Lage koi bhi dafa, padeh koi bhi case
Hoke rahenge kalesh
Tera baap hoon na laga race
Stop looking at my f*cking face

Meri shakal pe mat ja pandu, main kya hoon tujhe bata doon
Bholi bali surat par shakal pe mat ja
Meri shakal pe mat ja pandu, main kya hoon tujhe bata doon

Tuhi bacha le har har gange
